Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:38.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91802,98142}{\i1}Raised in a poor family which she has to support,\Nnot discouraged by the constant hardships of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:98142,101979}{\i1}a girl who loves to sing\Nand decided to live by singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:101979,103356}{\i1}Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:50.61,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104398,110613}{\i1}On the other hand, grown up in a wealthy family,\Nenjoying a facilitated path to stardom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.24,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:110613,113241}{\i1}a girl who takes the most\Neffective route to reach her goals,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:113241,114909}{\i1}Kōda Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:59.91,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:114909,119914}{\t(3055,5055,3,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)\fad(0,400)}— Episode 24 —\NThe Secret Is Out{NOTE:第24話\\N知らせた秘密}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:02.58,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:120248,122583}Thank you all for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:06.58,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:122583,126587}I'd like to release a certain information about\Ntwo singers who are now gaining popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:10.17,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:126587,130174}Something that will turn the lives of\NMine Nozomi and Kōda Miki upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:12.84,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:130174,132843}There is a secret behind\Nthe birth of these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.17,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:132843,134178}What kind of secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.01,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:134178,136013}Are they siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.80,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:136013,136806}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.35,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:136806,140351}I'll tell you everything,\Nbut I have to start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.06,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:140351,142061}Let me start with Kōda Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:25.43,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:142061,145439}She's not the daughter\Nof the great industrialist we all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:28.77,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:145439,148776}In reality, she is a daughter of an\Noden stand owner who lives in the slums.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.48,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:150653,153489}As for the other girl, Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:38.24,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:153489,158244}She's the rightful heiress to the Kōda Family.\NThe girls were swapped at their birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.20,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:158703,160204}Swapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.66,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:160204,161664}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.54,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:161664,163541}That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.83,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:163541,165835}But if it's true…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.25,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:166168,168254}I'm sorry, but I can't\Ngive you any more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:52.38,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:168254,172383}But I want to introduce myself. I am the sister\Nof the famous songwriter, Nohara Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.84,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:172383,175845}Now that you know who I am,\NI think you can believe my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.55,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:176262,178556}Hold still for the camera, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:16.03,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:190067,196032}{\an2\fad(1500,0)\fs40}The secret of the births of\NKōda Miki and Mine Nozomi\N{\fs33}Nohara Jun's sister's astonishing confession
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:20.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:197325,200036}T-That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.87,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:200661,202872}Try to calm down, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:204248,206083}They're saying\NI'm not your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.04,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:206083,207043}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:32.17,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:207877,212173}No one knows better than me who my daughter is.\NYou must not listen to their lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:212173,213049}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:38.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:213799,218971}The exchange took place in the hospital\Nand babies are all alike. It's plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.55,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:218971,220556}No, it's not. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.01,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:221307,224018}You were born in the Tonan Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.52,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:224018,227521}It's the best hospital in the city and certainly\Nnot a place where the poor can set foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.73,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:227521,230733}It's evident that it's the work of someone\Nwho is envious of your popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:55.02,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:231859,235029}Someone who can't bear to see\Nyou succeed and getting famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:235029,238449}Do you seriously think it's someone\Nwho wants to hinder me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:239325,241077}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.62,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:241077,242620}What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:05.74,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:242620,245748}People who appear on TV once or twice\Nand realize they can't succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:245748,247458}often resort to such games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.46,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:247458,249460}You know who this reminds me of?\NMine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:250127,251462}Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.46,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:252254,254465}Miss, there are people who want\Nto have an interview with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.80,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:255007,257802}They're from press.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.47,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:257802,259470}Oh, we'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.76,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:260304,262765}Do you understand?\NYou are a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.60,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:262765,264600}You can't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.97,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:264600,266977}For now, let your mom\Nhandle the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:35.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:270481,275236}It's true. If you want to become a star,\Nyou have to eliminate your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:275236,278239}{\i1}It's not so strange for Mine Nozomi\Nto try to create a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:278239,280908}{\i1}But this is just too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:280908,282993}{\i1}I won't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.62,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:286122,287623}You won't believe what I heard—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.91,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:287623,288916}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.92,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:290042,292920}Excuse me, where can I find\NMine Nozomi-san's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.79,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:292920,294797}We live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.75,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:294797,297758}Oh, you're her siblings?\NI'd like to talk to your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.00,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:297758,299009}She's not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.72,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:299009,301720}She went to the hospital\Nto get medicine for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.68,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:301720,303681}I see. Where is that hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.05,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:303681,305057}It's the one just beyond the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.30,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:305057,306308}Gotcha. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.60,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:307893,309603}What's your name, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.35,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:309603,311355}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.69,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:312148,314692}Sis is totally a star now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:314692,315901}Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.82,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:315901,317820}Here, the secret\Nof Nozomi-chan's birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.82,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:317820,318821}That must be it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.07,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:318821,320072}Let's see… hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.61,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:320072,321615}Whoa! Kōda's family empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.82,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{TIME:321615,322825}Hey, Kazuo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.24,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:322825,325244}No gossiping about\NNozomi-chan, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.28,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:325244,326287}Let's go, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.37,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:326287,327371}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.87,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:327371,329874}Tonan General Hospital{NOTE:都南総合病院}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:332460,334920}{\i1}What… Where it'd come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:334920,337131}{\i1}Me and Miki-san\Nexchanged in the cradles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:337131,338424}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:340009,343512}Why would Nohara-san's sister wait for 17 years\Nbefore going public with something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:343512,345931}This is… This is such nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:345931,347349}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:347349,348726}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:349560,351103}{\i1}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:351103,352521}{\i1}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:352521,354523}{\i1}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:56.27,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:355191,356275}Mine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.44,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:356275,358444}Here's your medicine, Mine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:358444,359904}Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:360321,361489}Sorry for spacing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:08.12,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:363741,368120}The doctor advises him to rest as much\Nas possible and avoid any stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:09.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:368120,369497}I understand. Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.41,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:369497,370414}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.00,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:376504,378005}It's Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.25,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:379215,381258}Mine-kun, we have\Na few questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.46,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:381258,382468}We're with the Weekly Punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.59,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:382468,385596}How do you feel about recent\Narticles about you in the newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:385596,386972}I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.14,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:386972,389141}Hey, hey, Mine-kun!\NJust a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.64,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:389141,391644}Do you have anything to say?\NEven single word will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:391644,392603}It's all slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.52,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:392603,393521}How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:394522,397066}Let me ask you, do you have\Nany proof to prove your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.36,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:397066,399360}Hmm, that's true,\Nwe don't exactly have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.69,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:399360,401695}But there's at least one person\Nwho claims that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:45.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:401695,405157}I only know that I am the daughter\Nof Mine Shinsuke and Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.86,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:405157,406867}Oh, in that case, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.03,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:406867,410037}I understand your side.\NBut the matter of Kōda Miki still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:410037,411747}Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:58.54,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:411747,418546}Yes. She thinks you created this scandal yourself\Nas a plan to bring down her popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:419088,421632}Me, bring Miki-san down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:02.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:421632,422800}That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.55,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:422800,426554}But to tell you the truth,\Nwe thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:427304,429598}Never in my life I'd do such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:429598,432726}Show some evidence before you\Nwrite such things in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:16.77,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:432726,436772}We don't have any evidence, but you're in\Na close relationship with Nohara Jun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:436772,438440}A close relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:22.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:438440,442570}I'd never asked Mr. Nohara to do anything for me.\NI don't have that sort of relationship with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:26.24,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:442570,446240}If what you say is true,\Nwho came up with it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:446240,448033}That's what I'd like to know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:448033,450578}Now, if you'll excuse me,\Nmy dad's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.83,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:453247,454832}Do you think she's honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:38.41,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:454832,458419}Please. Do you really believe those\Ncrocodile tears? We see them every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.83,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:458419,460838}In any case, we'll need some facts\Nto get to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.59,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{TIME:460838,463599}I'll just write about\NMine Nozomi's tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:481150,483861}Yes. I am Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:08.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:483861,488866}The one who's lived in this town forever,\Nborn to Mine Shinsuke and Shizuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:12.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:488866,492870}{\i1}This is my truth,\Neven if people tell me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.37,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:537456,538374}It's me, Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.25,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:538374,540250}Jun? What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.83,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:540918,542836}Don't play stupid.\NIt's all written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.42,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:543962,546423}Do not shout at me in the hall.\NWhat will the neighbors think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.46,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:546423,547466}Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.13,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:551512,554139}What were you thinking, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.55,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:554139,556558}Organizing a press conference?…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.06,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:556558,558060}Want a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.18,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:559770,561188}Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.06,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:561188,563065}Yes, I'm not deaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.94,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:563065,566944}Listen, it's not the first time that\Nthe newspapers openly attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.40,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:566944,569405}But this time you also expose yourself\Nthrough this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.15,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:569405,571156}I asked if you want some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.36,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:571156,572366}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:36.32,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:572366,576328}You may not be fully aware of this, but you can\Nend up in serious trouble because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.70,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:576328,577705}You can even end up in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.41,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:577705,579415}I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.45,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:579415,581458}What are you trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.00,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:581458,584002}Jun. I don't intend to cause\Nyou any more inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.00,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:584002,586004}Let me worry about my life myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.96,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:586004,587965}But you know, sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.50,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:587965,589508}I'm done listening to this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.92,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:589508,591927}Go away if you have\Nnothing more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.72,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:593345,595723}Very well. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:59.64,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:595723,599643}Jun! From now on, you can also\Nforget that we're siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.23,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:601770,604231}It'd be a hindrance\Nto your shining career, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.77,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:608444,610779}What, you forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.86,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:610779,614867}For all these years, you haven't\Nmarried anyone, you haven't eaten well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.24,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:614867,617244}you've been living\Nthis nasty lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.74,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:617244,619747}Who the hell are you\Ntrying to get revenge on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.99,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:620581,621999}Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:26.96,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:621999,626962}When a woman sacrifices her life in this way,\Nit can't be out of anything but vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.09,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:626962,630090}Don't concern yourself with this.\NIn the end, it's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.25,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:630090,631258}Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.25,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:631258,632259}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:633010,634219}Don't come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:42.47,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:637222,642478}However, you can't cut the blood ties so easily.\NThe two of us forever remain brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.52,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:644772,647524}Jun. I have nothing against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.98,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:647524,649985}But you could never possibly\Nunderstand my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.65,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:653739,657659}Sister. I hate you,\Nbut I still feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:03.95,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:659578,663957}{\i1}But I am really curious as to\Nhow this will affect their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:08.00,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:663957,668003}{\i1}Just when one of them is about\Nto become a great professional singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:14.42,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:670964,674426}Nozomi. Nozomi? Where's Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.76,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:674426,677763}She went to get you medicine.\NShe'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:24.56,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:679640,684561}You really can't do anything\Nwithout Nozomi, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.06,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:687815,690067}Hey, Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.06,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:690067,692069}Is what they write here true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:32.82,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:692069,692820}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.69,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:692820,694696}What if your father hears you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.82,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:694696,697825}But do reporters tell lies, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.74,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:697825,699743}No. Nozomi is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.82,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:699743,701829}She's your sister,\Nlike she's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.49,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:701829,704498}Yeah, it's just I don't know why,\Nbut it feels really complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:704498,706208}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:49.04,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:706750,709044}Just treat her the same way\Nyou always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.21,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:709044,710212}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:712297,714508}I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:714508,715425}How's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.67,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:715425,718679}He just fell asleep.\NWe'll give him pills later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:718679,719763}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:722432,723767}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.68,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:724226,725686}N-No, all's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.89,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:725686,726895}Right, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.18,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:726895,728188}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.06,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:728188,730065}All perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:13.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:730065,733735}I know everything.\NThere were reporters here, right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.32,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:733735,736321}No, not here, but they talked\Nwith Kazuo-chan and Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:736321,738156}Ah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.78,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:738156,739783}Thank goodness?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:741076,744788}The last thing Dad needs now\Nis to deal with such crappy rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.79,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:745330,746790}Thank you, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:747165,749710}Come on, Mom, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:749710,752504}No matter what anyone says,\NI was raised in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:752504,754298}I'm your and Dad's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.30,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:754882,756300}Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.92,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:756300,757926}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.76,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:762222,763765}Thank you, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:765142,766476}What's there to thank me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:766476,768061}You're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.89,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:768645,770898}She's our big sister, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.81,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:770898,771815}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:772482,775068}I can't believe you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.36,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:773233,776361}{\an8}Nozomi. Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:781241,782868}It's me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:05.45,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:782868,785454}Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:12.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:788916,792836}{\i1}Dad, no matter what,\NI am your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:793211,794713}{\i1}I'm my Dad's daughter.
Comment: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:23.41,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:803413,803413}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.58,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:803956,805582}Camera, action!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:03.41,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:840033,843412}It's false rumor. She's my own\Ndaughter, my flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.83,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:843412,845831}A mother can recognize her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:09.08,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:845831,849084}You tarnish my daughter's reputation.\NIf you don't stop, I'll sue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:849960,851336}I can't believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:16.75,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:852212,856758}That's not it yet.\NShe still has a lot to learn…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.30,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:859469,862306}No wonder, given that she's\Njust started her career.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.26,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:864308,865267}Good work, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.18,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:865267,868186}Ohh, Miki-chan,\Nif it isn't my favorite singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.39,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:868186,870397}Every day, you look more\Nand more like a real celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:35.52,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:870397,875527}But what is this story\Nthat you were swapped at birth—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.07,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:875527,878071}Shh. Let's talk outside, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.07,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:878071,880073}This isn't the best place\Nto discuss that topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.07,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:880073,882075}You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.95,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:886371,888957}Coffee, three times, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.62,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:888957,890625}Now, let's go back to the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.62,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:891335,893628}It's a real blow to the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.63,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:894046,895630}It's nothing but a bunch of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:59.46,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:895630,899468}Even so, such media attention\Nis not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.09,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:899468,902095}It may reflect bad\Non Miki-chan's career.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:06.55,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:902095,906558}Yes. Miki-chan is our goose that lays\Nthe golden eggs. We have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.85,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:906558,907851}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:13.14,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:907851,913148}I'm not opposed to tacky gossip,\Nas long as it increases sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.48,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:913148,917486}But suggesting that your daughter\Ncomes from a poor family is a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.61,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:917486,919613}This is an attack on Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.49,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:920155,921490}An attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.49,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:921490,923492}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:924701,926119}She's referring to Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.62,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:926787,930624}If I'm not mistaken, Mine Nozomi\Nwas an employee of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.12,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:930624,932125}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:35.92,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:932125,935921}She's jealous that Miki's made her debut earlier,\Nwhich is why she has resorted to such petty tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.96,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:936671,938965}She's willing to do\Nanything to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.59,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:938965,942594}In that case, why it was Nohara-kun's\Nsister that put the word out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.26,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:942594,944262}It's money.\NIt's all about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:48.14,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:944262,948141}That's why I am going\Nto file a lawsuit for defamation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:53.18,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:948141,953188}But you would only add fuel to the fire,\Ncausing even more gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.02,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:953188,956024}I have all the intention\Nto go all-out on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:16:00.48,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:956024,960487}Mr. President, please do your best\Nto suppress weekly magazines and media.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.73,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:960487,961738}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:961738,965450}Our conglomerate will prepare as much money\Nas it takes to get this issue sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.95,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:966034,967953}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.95,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:968787,971957}Miki-chan has finally started\Ngetting her recognition as a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.96,Default,Uchida President,0,0,0,,{TIME:972541,975961}We should eliminate all obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.55,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:983885,985554}Good evening.\NI'm from the National Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.85,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:988223,989850}Are you Nohara Michiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.89,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:989850,990892}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.89,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:990892,992894}I must ask you to accompany me\Nto the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.73,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:994312,995730}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.07,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000527,1002070}Take a sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:47.40,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004156,1007409}Let me get straight to the point.\NYou're detained on charges of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.62,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007409,1010620}defaming Kōda Miki at a press conference\Nyou organized some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.58,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010620,1013582}I'd like to ask you\Na few questions about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:58.04,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014207,1018044}First of all, what was the purpose\Nof that press conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:01.84,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018420,1021840}You also claimed that Kōda Miki\Nwasn't born to the Kōda family
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.75,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021840,1024759}and it is Mine Nozomi who is\Nthe rightful heiress instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.63,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024759,1026636}Is it the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.35,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032434,1035353}If it isn't, it's a very serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.35,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035353,1037355}Is it the truth,\Nor is it just worthless slander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.86,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039816,1041860}It's not slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.40,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041860,1044404}So you're claiming that\Nwhat you said was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.07,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044404,1046072}I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.65,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047741,1049659}That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.91,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049659,1050911}The exchange is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.91,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051828,1053914}And how could you\Npossibly know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.04,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055290,1057042}How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059002,1061213}Because I'm the one\Nwho'd swapped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:46.55,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061213,1066551}The day Kōda Miki and Mine Nozomi were born,\NI swapped their name tags, right in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.55,Default,Police man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071681,1073558}Tell me more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.73,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084027,1087739}When I was born,\NJapan was torn by war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:11.11,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087739,1091117}Right after my younger brother Jun\Nwas born, our father had to go to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.95,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091117,1093954}After his departure, our life\Nbecame more and more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:18.66,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093954,1098667}Once the war is over, our weak mother had\Nto go around selling soap door to door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:22.71,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098667,1102712}I was going to school while singing\Nlullabies to my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.17,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102712,1105173}It wasn't a merry life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:31.59,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105173,1111596}As I was about to graduate, I started to work\Nas an apprentice nurse at Tonan Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:39.52,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111596,1119521}My wish was to be able to help ill people, to ease\Ntheir suffering, as any good nurse should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.64,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119521,1122649}It was such a nice feeling,\NI thought I'd stay a nurse forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:46.27,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122649,1126278}One day I met a young patient\Nwho broke his legs on skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.28,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126278,1129281}That man came from a wealthy family\Nthat could afford such luxuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:52.03,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129281,1132033}He was from a world entirely\Ndifferent from the one I lived in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:56.53,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132033,1136538}Yet before I knew it, we started\Nto have fun taking long, long walks together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.95,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136538,1137956}My first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:01.37,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137956,1141376}A world of fables that I should\Nnever have ventured to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.79,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141376,1143795}But I didn't know it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.71,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143795,1146715}I was just a plain, timid girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:10.96,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146715,1150969}And above all,\NI really believed in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.34,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150969,1154347}Then he whispered\Nthe magic word: marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:18.56,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154347,1158560}He studied at a top university and\Nwas about to work for a top company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.39,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158560,1162397}But above all, he was going\Nto be my husband. I was crazy with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.77,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162397,1165775}But no dream lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.02,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165775,1169029}Suddenly, one day he came to see me\Nto ask to break the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:33.24,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169029,1173241}He told me that if he want to keep his career,\Nhe must ask to marry his boss' rich daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.99,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173241,1176995}and he couldn't take\Na poor girl like me as his bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:40.58,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176995,1180582}For a short period of my life,\NI had the chance to live the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.71,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180582,1183710}But it didn't take long for life\Nto come and kick me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.88,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183710,1186880}It was just too cruel. I had realized\NI would never find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:54.30,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188840,1194304}That day, I was on duty in the delivery room\Nwhere two girls were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:57.43,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194304,1197432}Newborns do not have\Nthe opportunity to decide their destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:01.39,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197432,1201394}They cannot change the family\Nwhere they come to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.10,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201394,1204105}These two girls were born\Non the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.48,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204105,1206483}They hadn't had the power to decide\Nanything for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:10.69,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206483,1210695}Only a small tag attached to their feet decides\Nwhether their life will be hell or paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.86,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212447,1215867}Then I got a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:20.28,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215867,1220288}If God decides destiny,\NI will take my revenge by changing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:25.21,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220288,1225210}It was the only way I could laugh at God,\Nwho's been making fun of me my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.71,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227545,1230715}The same night I had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.72,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236554,1239724}At that time I was only 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.60,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243812,1246606}Nozomi-chan, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.60,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246606,1248608}You're so much stronger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255031,1256449}Yes, this is Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.36,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256449,1257367}Uchida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:00.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259536,1260954}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.46,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266000,1267460}Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269421,1271339}Nohara Michiko\Nswitched the babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.92,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271339,1274926}Are you serious?\NThe police?…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.34,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274926,1276344}It's the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.85,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282475,1283852}{\i1}Miki is not my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.35,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289441,1291359}{\i1}She's… not my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:34.36,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292861,1294362}Sumiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.78,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296573,1298783}Miki! Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:40.49,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298783,1300493}Get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.03,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300493,1302036}She's not my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302036,1304456}My real daughter is Mine Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.12,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304456,1305123}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.54,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305123,1307542}Sumiyo! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:50.58,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307542,1310587}Mine Nozomi… is my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.25,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310587,1312255}Mine Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:02.76,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318636,1322766}Mine-kun is rehearsing right now.\NPlease wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:37.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353755,1357133}{\i1}Dad… I'm your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:42.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357133,1362138}{\i1}My earliest memories are of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:44.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362138,1364891}{\i1}When you got home drunk,\Nyou always sang me the song about apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.89,0:22:48.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364891,1368353}{\i1}It was terrible,\Nbut also very nice at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:51.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368353,1371856}{\i1}I kept asking you again and again,\N"sing it another time",
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371856,1374234}{\i1}and you had\Nthis big smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:57.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374234,1377362}{\i1}Get well soon, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:23:00.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377362,1380698}{\i1}And let me hear the song\Nabout the apples again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:02.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380698,1382700}{\i1}I'm your child, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:08.66,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1386037,1388665}Really good, I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.29,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388665,1391292}Mine-kun, you got a phone call.
